  "_meta": {
    "description": "Curated ElevenLabs premade voices for V4 persona voice acquisition. Premade voices work on all ElevenLabs tiers including free. Library voices (like Rachel) require a paid plan. Each entry has voice_id, display name, and descriptive tags that Gemini matches against persona briefs.",
